title: Female CEO Love Me
overview: Xia Meng Wei (Yang Xin Ying) is a female CEO who is domineering, intelligent, but often utters hurtful words. Uniquely, the CEO fell in love with Gu Yan (Cai Yi Jia) at first sight. Whereas Gu Yan was just a counter boy who had many skills. Xia Meng Wei tried various ways to win Gu Yan's heart. Did the CEO win the employee's heart?
